config.title: Monitoring OpenAI  gpt-4o-mini  API Costs and Token Usage
config.sqlQuery:
WITH token_data AS (
  -- Step 1: Aggregate completion and prompt tokens
  SELECT 'total_completion_tokens' AS metric, 
         SUM((attributes->'response_data'->'usage'->>'completion_tokens')::FLOAT) AS value
  FROM records
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 'total_prompt_tokens' AS metric, 
         SUM((attributes->'response_data'->'usage'->>'prompt_tokens')::FLOAT) AS value
  FROM records
),
cost_data AS (
  -- Step 2: Calculate costs and exclude 'total' from percentage calculations
  SELECT
    metric,
    value,
    ROUND((value / (SELECT SUM(value) FROM token_data WHERE metric != 'total')) * 100, 1) AS percentage_of_tokens, -- Correct token percentage
    CASE
      WHEN metric = 'total_completion_tokens' THEN ROUND(value * 0.0000006, 6) -- Cost for completion tokens (scaled correctly)
      WHEN metric = 'total_prompt_tokens' THEN ROUND(value * 0.00000015, 6) -- Cost for prompt tokens (scaled correctly)
      ELSE NULL
    END AS cost
  FROM token_data
),
final_data AS (
  -- Step 3: Add the total row, exclude it from percentage calculations
  SELECT
    metric,
    value,
    percentage_of_tokens,
    ROUND(cost, 6) AS cost,
    NULL AS percentage_of_costs -- Placeholder for percentage of costs
  FROM cost_data
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'total',
    SUM(value) AS value,
    NULL AS percentage_of_tokens, -- Exclude total from token percentage
    ROUND(SUM(cost), 6) AS cost,
    NULL AS percentage_of_costs -- Exclude total from cost percentage
  FROM cost_data
)
-- Step 4: Calculate percentage of costs excluding the total
SELECT
  metric,
  value,
  percentage_of_tokens,
  cost,
  CASE
    WHEN metric != 'total' THEN ROUND((cost / (SELECT SUM(cost) FROM cost_data WHERE metric != 'total')) * 100, 1) -- Exclude 'total' from cost percentage
    ELSE NULL
  END AS percentage_of_costs
FROM final_data
ORDER BY CASE WHEN metric = 'total' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, metric;

/*
Useful Snippets:
 attributes->'response_data'->'usage'->>'total_tokens' IS NOT NULL
*/
